{"tid":2220332,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大圍跑馬地鴨脷洲長沙灣半日間共四宗墮樓","createTime":"2020-09-27T14:43:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T14:57:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32ecf95e43f309b7d4d9b8d614888cc18c6db987","tid":2220332,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:43:47.000Z","msg":"早上8時04分，大圍美松苑麗松閣有人墮樓，途人發現並報警，救援人員到場後將中年女子送往威爾斯親王醫院搶救，惜最終證實不治，現場留有血迹，一副假牙及口罩。<br />\n<br />\n另外，早上9時44分，跑馬地毓秀街毓成大廈，一名79歲老翁從睡房一躍而下，有人發現後報警，救援人員趕到現場，老翁當場證實不治。現場一部電單車遭壓毀，據了解老翁患有身體病及精神病，警方正調查事件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200927/ITTQ5OGGHBEFPMCTOOM5ULCD6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200927%2FITTQ5OGGHBEFPMCTOOM5ULCD6I%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=4cf34703\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200927%2FITTQ5OGGHBEFPMCTOOM5ULCD6I%2F&h=8dba822b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200927/ITTQ5OGGHBEFPMCTOOM5ULCD6I/</a><br />\n<br />\n下午2時許，警方接報一名女子從深水埗青山道複合大樓一高處墮下，倒卧一間餐廳的後巷位置，消防及救護員接報到場將傷者救起，並經餐廳抬上救護車，送往明愛醫院搶救，可惜最終不治，警方正調查女子墮樓原因。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200927/NPCQAIHHDBADJOXN7NUONK62IM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200927%2FNPCQAIHHDBADJOXN7NUONK62IM%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUh5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=bd5352cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20200927%2FNPCQAIHHDBADJOXN7NUONK62IM%2F&h=207dfa74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20200927/NPCQAIHHDBADJOXN7NUONK62IM/</a><br />\n<br />\n香港仔鴨脷洲有人墮樓。今午(27日)2時19分，鴨脷洲邨利滿樓有男子從高處墮下，頭部重創倒臥地上，多名街坊見狀，大驚報警。救護員到場，立即將已陷入昏迷的事主送院搶救，惜最終傷重不治。警方於現場沒有檢獲遺書，經初步調查，證實死者姓李(57歲)，相信他從上址一走廊墮下，惟死因有待驗屍後確定。現場所見，地上留下一隻相信屬於事主的涼鞋。其後，事主親友接獲通知趕到現場，得知情況後，一度傷心痛哭，要他人安撫。"},{"pid":"7ad22c1ec972f2f16e6991f140d968c1abe2f684","tid":2220332,"uid":49753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:44:34.000Z","msg":"死黑驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c871f66b61e4d3f07bc603b8265feb16d32d9e5c","tid":2220332,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:44:42.000Z","msg":"今午(27日)12時29分，一名男子於葵盛西邨3座高處墮下，倒臥地上重創昏迷。救援人員接報趕至，將事主送院搶救，惜返魂乏術，現場留有一攤血漬及一隻波鞋。警方於現場有檢獲遺書，經初步調查，證實死者姓張(44歲)，相信他從上址一走廊墮下，惟死因有待驗屍後確定。據悉，張因生活問題不開心輕生。"},{"pid":"ec2a5b746c7cadabf7700b3bbb100bc0ac90b7dd","tid":2220332,"uid":338439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:45:19.000Z","msg":"Popo"},{"pid":"fcd6dfc88e940e2023d34f63ae7cfa5e7d7bd598","tid":2220332,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:50:21.000Z","msg":"香港真係一塊&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b37dd342e3271054855fe40cd63eb142e0bbf569","tid":2220332,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adc1c73f5e9dcb3ebd32ff3b9a877dcc6d1de34","tid":2220332,"uid":134474,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"要佢哋生存慘過死，其他幾時有安樂死，好似瑞士咁，喺一間好平凡房間度，飲一杯無味道嘅藥，之後慢慢睡著，安祥離世<br />\n<br />\n我唔會怪罪輕生嘅人，唔係佢地嘅錯"},{"pid":"e3cc3b269d05b801a1141c54cc7a57e793f81619","tid":2220332,"uid":78703,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:51:05.000Z","msg":"手足 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.g